-- ============================================================================
-- Seed: DACH universities from the hipo/university-domains-list dataset
--   (https://github.com/hipo/university-domains-list, static JSON snapshot).
--
-- Populates public.universities with name/country/email_domains for every
-- Germany/Austria/Switzerland entry (443 rows), so onboarding + email-domain
-- verification (link_university_email) work for students outside Marburg.
--
-- source='hipo', external_ref=<primary domain> (stable key across re-runs).
-- Idempotent: ON CONFLICT (source, external_ref) DO UPDATE.
--
-- Dedup guard: skips any hipo row whose email_domains overlap a university
-- already seeded from a richer source (e.g. scraper:marburg), so the existing
-- Marburg row -- with its faculty/degree_program/catalog_course tree already
-- attached -- never gets a duplicate sibling entry in the picker.
-- ============================================================================

